{"tid":839894,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"前俄超MVP外借加盟港超升班馬凱景 曾助球會奪歐協盃及歐超盃冠軍","createTime":"2018-09-28T09:30:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-09T14:53:44.000Z","uid":9030,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"beedcd92310486e03f15647b7c8fad3735b7b7fa","tid":839894,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T09:30:13.000Z","msg":"凱景主教練馮凱文證實，從傑志借用前南韓國腳金東進。至於金東進能否趕及下周日（30日）對理文一仗正選上陣，「馮Sir」則表示不排除其可能性，但基於金東進由周三（26日）才開始參與球隊操練，因此要視乎情況再決定是否讓他擔任正選。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20180928/photo/bkn-20180928151354005-0928_00882_001_01b.jpg?20180928152938\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20180928%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180928151354005-0928_00882_001_01b.jpg%3F20180928152938&h=02b9e90d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"055279827f1bfae1bdb670fa5092ec27f8af3edc","tid":839894,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T09:30:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e422e0196f19e42afe7a5bae74a850e42c7665aa","tid":839894,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T09:31:42.000Z","msg":"金東進2006年世界盃完結後加盟俄超球會辛尼特，並簽訂三年合約，並在2007年協助辛尼特奪得聯賽冠軍，而他同時當選俄超年度最佳球員，隨後他於2008年再度協助球會奪得歐洲足協盃及歐洲超級盃冠軍。"},{"pid":"eda4e0e9292cf83dd6b4d4fce657b0f67fc23e84","tid":839894,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"055279827f1bfae1bdb670fa5092ec27f8af3edc","tid":839894,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T09:30:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T09:32:42.000Z","msg":"港超升班馬都簽到咁有卡士既國際球星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcafb8aaec40f23014faf130a91c923cb77967b0","tid"